des: Maybe you’re getting coal this year or maybe you’ve been as sweet as a gumdrop, there’s only one way to find out! This app for all ages will walk you through a series of fun questions to let you know where you are on Santa’s list. But be sure to check back to see if you’re still on the nice list, you might even get something amazing under your tree this year!
